  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Create. Edit. Share. </h2>Video editing, made for everyone<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Kickstart Your Projects </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Save Time With Thousands of Shareable Video Intros </h2>Discover and create attention-grabbing video intros alongside our community of creatives. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/8c99d3734c1882025e1c4d35d06216fe.avif?t=1754574262\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Simple Tools, Powerful Effects</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mask Designer</h2>Remove unwanted objects, or composite clips together. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/3846f8a80092247cc32dbb8e70f30268.avif?t=1754574262\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Title Designer</h2>Choose from drag-and-drop presets or get creative with an array of gradient, border, and shadow tools. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/3文字設計師.JPG?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PIP Designer</h2>Use animated stickers, shapes, and callouts to grab your viewers’ attention. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/4_子母畫面設計師.JPG?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > AI Motion Tracking </h2>Add text or graphics that automatically follow the motion of any object. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/d61a36120f643aa2b68c449442f38ec8.avif?t=1754574262\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > AI Object Detection </h2>Instantaneously create masks with automatic object selection for cars, people, pets, and more. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/97aa8af91677fc3316f5a129c6a0896b.avif?t=1754574262\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Your Footage, Your Way </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyframes</h2>Position, scale, and rotate objects to create custom animations. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/8關鍵畫格.JPG?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Action Cam</h2>Apply preset lens corrections to remove fisheye distortion, change video speed, and stabilize unwanted camera shake in just a few clicks. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/46b583a9509742ee201b222bace1a6bd.avif?t=1754574262\" width=590 height=368 /></span></h2></ul>",
